Merb Uploader

This application is meant to be run as an uploading server for long running files. 

To begin, this application follows the path set out by Christopher Stuss
http://www.scribelabs.com/2007/10/18/file-uploads-via-merb-inside-a-rails-application-part-1-of-3/

There are assuredly going to be changes to the basic assumptions.